productReviews.reviewText: I tried to shred it but got watermelon all over it.
heard about this on powerviolence radio, decided to give it a try.
My neighbor Lonnie has one of these. She works as a hobbit and she says it looks microscopic.
My co-worker Archer has one of these. He says it looks crooked.
This e-business works certainly well. It accidentally improves my baseball by a lot.
